Description: SafeUrl: link analyzer on Python
        ================================
        Simple and clever analyzer, decoder, encoder ... urls on python, using requests
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/safeurl.svg
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/safeurl
        
        
